293
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,700
That man sure works fast.

294
00:15:13,070 --> 00:15:14,170
What a guy.

295
00:15:22,620 --> 00:15:23,950
Good evening.

296
00:15:26,290 --> 00:15:28,260
