The exact response I was expecting!

298
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:31,980
Good!

299
00:15:34,530 --> 00:15:37,830
Wow! This is delicious!
I am so impressed!

300
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:39,900
- You'll make a good wife, Nana.
- No... Umm...

301
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:42,230
You have the same name,
but what a difference!

302
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,960
Thanks for the compliment.
I made that.

303
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,370
Figures. I thought it was a bit...

304
