- I don't wanna hear!

314
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:11,830
I ran away from home.

315
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:13,490
I told you,
I don't wanna hear it!

316
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,330
Nana!

317
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,600
I have no attraction to
my hometown, whatsoever.

318
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:19,070
