I'm totally used to this.

322
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:31,240
Don't expect any hospitality,
but you can stay here if you like.

323
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:33,910
Thanks. You're so kind...

324
00:16:33,990 --> 00:16:35,620
I won't have it.

325
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:37,820
